  "title": "Junior Conveyancing Lawyer - 5 days / Central area [2683]",
  "description": "<p><strong>WhatsApp: +65 90820021 (Kyler)</strong><br /><strong>Email: kylergan.supreme@gmail.com</strong></p><p>Working Days: 5 days<br />Working Timing: 9:00 am to 6:00 pm<br />Working Location: Telok Ayer Street<br />Starting Salary: $4000 - $5,500</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities & Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and review legal documents related to property transactions. These documents include sale and purchase agreements and loan agreements.</li><li>You will provide advice to clients on all aspects of buying or selling property. This includes legal issues, financial considerations, and contract matters.</li><li>Engage in negotiations with the other party’s lawyer for the Option to Purchase (OTP). Provide advice to clients on the conveyancing process and their rights and obligations.</li><li>Liaise with various parties involved in the transaction, including real estate agents, mortgage lenders, and other relevant stakeholders.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications and Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Law </li><li>0-3 years of Post-Qualification Experience (PQE) in conveyancing or related legal work.</li><li>Familiarity with property laws and conveyancing procedures.</li></ul><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | 14C7279</strong><br /><strong>Gan Kai Le | R23112683</strong></p>",
